            "title": "Thibault Sottiaux · @thsottiaux · Codex & ChatGPT, OpenAI",
            "text": "🔗 Post \"Prepare your sunglasses. Sol is coming. 😎\" — With 4,150 likes, this teaser from an OpenAI Codex team member amplifies the Sol launch narrative. The \"sunglasses\" framing signals brightness/intensity — consistent with a step-change in output quality or reasoning depth, not just a speed upgrade. \"准备好你的墨镜，Sol来了。😎\"——来自OpenAI Codex团队成员的这条预告获4,150个点赞，放大了Sol的发布叙事。\"墨镜\"框架暗示亮度/强度——与输出质量或推理深度的跨越式升级相一致，而非仅仅是速度提升。 ---",
