            "text": "Guests: Angela (Head of Product, Claude Platform) and Caitlin (Head of Engineering, Claude Platform) Host: Dan Shipper Link: YouTube --- Core Argument / 核心论点 The Claude platform team's core thesis is that platform evolution follows a single through-line: as models become more capable and autonomous, the right platform response is to raise the abstraction level while preserving modularity. A completion endpoint was right in 2022. Managed Agents with memory, code execution, file systems, and multi-agent orchestratio…",
