            "text": "Swyx is emphatic: Codex is \"completely unrecognizable from 3 months ago\" — the team went \"extreme founder mode\" on it. Separately, the head of AI Govtech in Singapore is projecting 1.3 billion agents deployed in the country within 2 years, a number Swyx flagged as a real signal of how aggressively governments outside the US are moving on agentic infrastructure. Swyx（AI.Engineer、Latent Space、Cognition、Temporal）Swyx语气强烈：Codex\"和3个月前完全判若云泥\"——团队进入了\"极端创始人模式\"全力冲刺。另外，新加坡AI政务科技主管预测该国未来2年内将部署13亿个agent，Swyx将这一数字标记为一个真实信号，反映出…",
