            "title": "Dan Shipper (CEO at Every)",
            "text": "Dan Shipper: \"Codex-native apps are the future.\" He also published a full deep-dive on Every's attempt to build an agent-as-a-service platform on OpenClaw — two big learnings flagged: OpenClaw's architecture does something fundamentally different from a simple API wrapper, and the experience of building on it surfaced assumptions about agent infrastructure that turned out to be wrong. Dan Shipper（Every CEO）Dan Shipper：\"Codex原生应用是未来。\"他还发布了一篇完整的深度复盘，记录了Every在OpenClaw上构建agent-as-a-service平台的尝试——标注了两个重大收获：OpenClaw的架构做…",
