            "title": "Sam Altman (OpenAI CEO)",
            "text": "Sam Altman noted that he appreciates how seriously the OpenAI team takes safety reports — \"even when the answer turns out to be 'I got used to the model's behavior.'\" Brief, but telling: internal safety culture requires taking reports seriously even when they resolve benignly. Sam Altman（OpenAI CEO）Sam Altman表示，他很欣赏OpenAI团队对安全报告的认真态度——\"即使最终的答案是'我已经习惯了模型的这种行为'\"。言简意赅，但意味深长：内部安全文化要求认真对待每一份报告，即便最终证明是虚惊一场。 ---",
